Ruth Franklin's Artistic Touch https://www.ruthfranklinbonnaz.com/posts/educationalvhs/ -<p>The Artistic Touch School of Embroidery Videos give all of the information needed to learn to operate a chain stitch embroidery machine.</p>
<p>Volume 1 includes Ruth Franklin instructing her student Leah through the embroidery operation basics. Volumes 2 and 3 include Ruth Franklin demonstrating more advanced techniques. All together they cover everything that was taught to her students in person.</p>
